{"word":"Condescension of God","slug":"condescension-of-god","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Condescension of God</b> In reasoning with His creatures:<br/> - Sets forth His reasons for sending the flood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=6&verse=13'>Gen 6:13</a> <br/> - Enters into covenant with Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=21'>Gen 15:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=22'>Gen 18:22</a> <br/> - Indulges Abraham's intercession for Sodom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=33'>Gen 18:33</a> <br/> - Warns Abimelech in a dream<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=7'>Gen 20:7</a> <br/> - Reasons with Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=17'>Exo 4:17</a> <br/> - Sends flesh to the Israelites in consequence of their murmuring<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=12'>Exo 16:12</a> <br/> - Indulges Moses' prayer to behold His glory<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=23'>Exo 33:23</a> <br/> - Indulges Gideon's tests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=40'>Jdg 6:40</a> <br/> - Reasons with Job<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=38'>Job 38</a> <br/> - Invites sinners, saying, &#187;Come now, and let us reason together&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=1&verse=20'>Isa 1:20</a> <br/> - Expostulates with backsliding Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=41&verse=24'>Isa 41:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=43&verse=19'>Isa 43:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=65&verse=16'>Isa 65:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=3&verse=15'>Jer 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=31'>Jer 4:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=34'>Jer 7:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=18&verse=32'>Eze 18:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=20'>Eze 33:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=2'>Hos 2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=9'>Mic 6:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=15'>Mal 3:15</a> <br/> Scriptures relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=6'>Psa 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=113&verse=6'>Psa 113:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=144&verse=3'>Psa 144:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=45&verse=11'>Isa 45:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=16'>Joh 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=5&verse=8'>Rom 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=2&verse=11'>Heb 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=6&verse=18'>Heb 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=4&verse=10'>1Jn 4:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=4&verse=19'>1Jn 4:19</a>"}]}